data.description: The Forest at Belvedere Plantation has a lovely updated 3 bedroom 2 bath with a substantial bonus room for sale! The beautiful kitchen has ample counter and cabinet space with new quartz countertops, large pantry, and stainless appliance. On the main floor, the primary suite has more than enough room for a king-sized bed, has a vaulted ceiling, laminate flooring with a tiled walk-in shower, garden tub, newly tiled floor, and walk-in closet. LVP in the living area, roof, counters, water heater, and more have been added in the past few years. Gather around the fireplace in the living room which is a part of a well-functioning open floor plan.  Spend your afternoons in the all-weather room or on the patio enjoying nature and/or the golfer on the course behind the home.It is only about 10 miles to Topsail Island beaches, shops, and restaurants and less than a few miles from Hampstead restaurants and shopping. Even the public Wildlife Landing is less than a ten minute drive! Conveniently located for an easy commute to New River Air Station, Camp Lejeune, CFCC, UNC-W, Corning, and other employment opportunities, Jacksonville and Wilmington are a hop, skip, and a jump from Hampstead. Plus a home warranty!
